dcterms:description: UA-DETRAC is a benchmark dataset for multi-object detection and tracking, containing 100 sequences of vehicle tracking scenarios, with 60 sequences for training and the rest for testing. The dataset is designed to evaluate the performance of detection and tracking algorithms.
dcterms:title: UA-DETRAC
